{{main|1920年路易斯安那飓风}}
9月16日，[[哥伦比亚|哥伦比亚]]西北方向的[[热带扰动|扰动天气区]]发展成热带低气压。气旋起初强度偏弱，[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]][[尼加拉瓜|尼加拉瓜]]时依然是热带低气压，但在经过[[洪都拉斯湾|洪都拉斯湾]]期间得以增强，在登陆[[尤卡坦半岛|尤卡坦半岛]]前成为热带风暴。进入[[墨西哥湾|墨西哥湾]]后，气旋在朝[[罗盘方位|西北偏北]]移动的同时快速强化，达到风力时速160公里的二级飓风强度后从[[路易斯安那州|路易斯安那州]][[霍玛_(路易斯安那州)|霍玛]]附近登陆。接下来风暴在陆地上空急剧减弱，最终于9月23日在东[[堪萨斯州|堪萨斯州]]上空逐渐消散。<ref name="HURDAT" />

飓风逼近[[美国墨西哥湾沿岸地区|美国墨西哥湾沿岸地区]]之际，估计[[加尔维斯顿岛|加尔维斯顿岛]]有4500人被迫撤离<ref name="4,500">{{cite news | url = http://article.archive.nytimes.com/1920/09/22/107002526.pdf?AWSAccessKeyId=AKIAJBTN455PTTBQQNRQ&Expires=1482855918&Signature=d2hRXY0ifp9y9D90lrYDPjhprMM%3D | title = 4,500 Move Out of Galveston | newspaper = [[纽约时报|The New York Times]] | date = 1920-09-21 | location = Galveston, Texas | accessdate = 2016-12-27 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20161227162131/http://article.archive.nytimes.com/1920/09/22/107002526.pdf?AWSAccessKeyId=AKIAJBTN455PTTBQQNRQ&Expires=1482855918&Signature=d2hRXY0ifp9y9D90lrYDPjhprMM%3D | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-12-27 }}</ref>，另有多地采取包括疏散人员在内的多种预防措施<ref name="Inhabitants">{{cite news | title = Ready to Move Inhabitants | accessdate = 2016-12-27 | newspaper = The Washington Reporter | page = 10 | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=30RiAAAAIBAJ&sjid=0XUNAAAAIBAJ&pg=5475,5006064&dq=hurricane&hl=en | date = 1920-09-21 | location = Galveston, Texas | archive-date = 2021-01-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210119093423/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=30RiAAAAIBAJ&sjid=0XUNAAAAIBAJ&pg=5475%2C5006064&dq=hurricane&hl=en | dead-url = no }}</ref>。风暴登陆时在大范围沿海地区产生狂风，将树木连根拔起，还对部分民房和[[基础设施|基础设施]]构成破坏<ref name="documentation">{{cite report | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/metadata_dec12.html | display-authors = etal | title = Documentation of Atlantic Tropical Cyclones Changes in HURDAT | author = Christopher W. Landsea | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150930195553/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/metadata_dec12.html | date = 2012-12 | work = Atlantic Oceanographic and Meteorological Laboratory | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | accessdate = 2016-12-27 | location = Miami, Florida | archivedate = 2015-09-30 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。暴雨在[[罗伯茨代尔|罗伯茨代尔]]产生的降水最多，达300毫米<ref name="rainfall">{{cite report | title = Rainfall Associated With Hurricanes (And Other Tropical Disturbances) | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/1956NHRPreportNo3.pdf | publisher = United States Weather Bureau's National Hurricane Research Project | accessdate = 2016-12-27 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304065316/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/1956NHRPreportNo3.pdf | author = R.W. Schoner | author2 = S. Molansky | last-author-amp = yes | page = 63 | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = no | format = PDF | date =  }}</ref>。暴雨还将铁轨冲毁，引发多起铁路事故<ref name="Sweeps">{{cite news | title = Great Hurricane is Sweeping the Atlantic Coast | date = 1920-09-22 | location = Galveston, Texas; New Orleans, Louisiana | page = 1 | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=DjdUAAAAIBAJ&sjid=TjoNAAAAIBAJ&pg=2737,633684&dq=hurricane&hl=en | accessdate = 2016-12-27 | newspaper = Greensburg Daily Tribune | archive-date = 2020-11-06 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201106103913/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=DjdUAAAAIBAJ&sjid=TjoNAAAAIBAJ&pg=2737%2C633684&dq=hurricane&hl=en | dead-url = no }}</ref>。气旋在美国墨西哥湾沿岸地区共导致一人死亡，损失总额约为145万美元<ref name="documentation" />。
